703785f-a.title: Brooklyn: Coney Island Avenue - Avenue O
703785f-a.text:
1888-1892 Coney Island Ave., west side, between Aves. O and P, showing
at the right the hommme f Daniel Barre (No. 1888), and at the left the home of
Stephen Williamson which was erected by him in 1860.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
